des: Ask "Urgent Care" is the Urgent Care Clinic of Lincoln's Alexa skill enabling users to find out the current wait time, medical conditions we treat, and services we offer. The skill also covers procedures done at the clinic, and tests available at the clinic. Alexa can even arrange a phone call or a call back if the clinic is closed.
